channel.title: How to start a server
channel.description:
Ok heres a tut made by OWNER GODZ ENJOY HOPFULLY THIS HELPS STEP ONE- First you will need the highest updates on java ill give u downloading links.
WinZip 12 for Windows 2000/XP/Vista [url=http://www.download.com/WinZip/3000-...-10003164.html]http://www.download.com/WinZip/3000-...-10003164.html[/url]
WinRar 3.80 for Windows 95/98/Me/NT/2000/XP/Vista [url=http://www.download.com/WinRAR/3000-...-10007677.html]http://www.download.com/WinRAR/3000-...-10007677.html[/url]
JDK 6 Update 21 with NetBeans 6.5 [url=http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/netbeans.html]http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/netbeans.html[/url]
JDK 6 Update 21 with Java EE [url=https://cds.sun.com/is-bin/INTERSHOP...-CDS_Developer]https://cds.sun.com/is-bin/INTERSHOP...-CDS_Developer[/url]
STEP TWO- Now time to download a source for your server.
TestScape - [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=VC3TV8XY]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=VC3TV8XY[/url] CheezScape 80 - [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=8MF4EQBL]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=8MF4EQBL[/url] Project 16 Version 6 Edit 7 - [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=7DO6EFY7]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=7DO6EFY7[/url] There are also lots more but these are my best recommended ones.
STEP THREE- Get a winzip extracter for source if u don't have one you cna get one here.
WinRAR archiver - [url=http://www.rarlab.com/rar/wrar361.exe]http://www.rarlab.com/rar/wrar361.exe[/url]
STEP FOUR- Now that you got winzip downloaded extract the source and open it up. Right click the Compiler and click on edit. Erase everything inside of it and put this in it.
@echo off title yourservernamehere "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\java.exe" server pause
Now do the same thing to the Run.java and erase it all and put
@echo off title yourservernamehere java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server
STEP FIVE- Time to set up No-Ip. Go to [url=http://www.no-ip.com]www.no-ip.com[/url] and register. Once you have activated your account download the no-ip and on the site look for where it says host/redirects and create it like servernamehere.no-ip.whateveryouwant. After you are done open the no-ip thing that you downloaded and refresh it. Then your servername should pop up. Click the check box and exit out of it.
STEP SIX- Now it is time to redirect your router to do this is hard to explain so go to this recommended site
[url=http://www.portforward.com/]http://www.portforward.com/[/url]
FINAL STEP- Now you are done! So you can go to silab which link is [url=http://client.silabsoft.org/client.php]http://client.silabsoft.org/client.php[/url] type in your new servers ip which would be with the no-ip and then your in!
